# Samsung Sales Data Analysis (Power BI)

This project analyzes Samsung global sales data using Power BI to explore revenue trends, product performance, and customer insights.

## Tools Used
- Power BI
- Data Visualization
- Data Analysis

## Dataset
Samsung Global Sales Dataset containing sales information such as product category, revenue, customer age group, ratings, and return status.

## Dashboard Features
- Revenue analysis by country
- Revenue distribution by product category
- Yearly revenue trends (2021–2024)
- Customer age group analysis
- Product rating comparison
- Return status analysis

## Key Insight
Total Revenue Generated: **$22.91 Million**

